      <title>电动汽车制造商 Lion Electric 总裁离职，因该公司寻求现金流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lion-electric-s-president-is-gone-as-ev-maker-searches-for-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大电动巴士和卡车制造商 Lion Electric Co. 的总裁辞职，因为这家资金短缺的公司正在为维持生存而做最后的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lion-electric-s-president-is-gone-as-ev-maker-searches-for-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:10:33 GMT</pubDate>
